## Directory Structure

| Directory      | Purpose                                               |
|----------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| `systemrdl/`   | CSR / register map definitions (SystemRDL)            |
| `bsv/`         | RTL source (Bluespec SystemVerilog)                   |
| `tb/`          | Testbench & simulation (cocotb)                       |
| `lint/`        | RTL linting (Verilator, Verible, Spyglass)            |
| `constraints/` | SDC / XDC timing constraints                          |
| `synth/`       | Logic synthesis (Yosys, Design Compiler, Genus)       |
| `sta/`         | Static timing analysis (OpenSTA, PrimeTime)           |
| `pnr/`         | Place & route (OpenROAD, ICC2, Innovus)               |
| `power/`       | Power analysis                                        |
| `drc/`         | DRC / LVS checks (Magic, Calibre)                    |
| `cdc/`         | Clock domain crossing analysis                        |
{%- if enable_formal %}
| `formal/`      | Formal verification (SymbiYosys, JasperGold)          |
{%- endif %}
{%- if enable_fpga %}
| `fpga/`        | FPGA prototyping (Vivado, Quartus)                    |
{%- endif %}
| `doc/`         | Documentation                                         |
| `ci/`          | CI orchestration & GitLab CI pipeline                 |

## Quick Start

```bash
# Generate CSR maps and compile RTL
make csr rtl

# Run linting
make lint

# Run tests
make test

# Full default build (csr + rtl + lint + test + synth)
make all

# CI pipelines
make ci_quick   # lint → csr → rtl → test
make ci_full    # lint → csr → rtl → formal → test → synth → sta → power → pnr → drc
```

## Toolchain Requirements

### Open-Source

| Tool           | Purpose                        |
|----------------|--------------------------------|
| Bluespec (bsc) | BSV → Verilog compilation      |
| Verilator      | RTL linting & simulation       |
| Verible        | SystemVerilog linting / format |
| cocotb         | Python-based testbench         |
| Yosys          | Logic synthesis                |
| OpenSTA        | Static timing analysis         |
| OpenROAD       | Place & route                  |
| SymbiYosys     | Formal verification            |
| Magic          | DRC / LVS                      |

### Commercial (Optional)

| Tool               | Purpose              |
|--------------------|------------------------|
| Synopsys DC         | Logic synthesis       |
| Cadence Genus       | Logic synthesis       |
| Synopsys PrimeTime  | Static timing analysis|
| Synopsys ICC2       | Place & route         |
| Cadence Innovus     | Place & route         |
| Synopsys SpyGlass   | Lint / CDC            |
| Cadence JasperGold  | Formal verification   |
| Siemens Calibre     | DRC / LVS             |
| Xilinx Vivado       | FPGA synthesis & PnR  |
| Intel Quartus       | FPGA synthesis & PnR  |

## Make Targets Reference

| Target     | Description                                      |
|------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| `all`      | Default: csr rtl lint test synth                  |
| `csr`      | Generate CSR register maps                        |
| `rtl`      | Compile RTL (BSV → Verilog)                       |
| `lint`     | RTL linting                                       |
| `formal`   | Formal verification                               |
| `test`     | Run testbench / simulation                        |
| `synth`    | Logic synthesis                                   |
| `sta`      | Static timing analysis                            |
| `power`    | Power analysis                                    |
| `pnr`      | Place & route                                     |
| `drc`      | DRC / LVS checks                                  |
| `fpga`     | FPGA prototyping                                  |
| `doc`      | Generate documentation                            |
| `ci_quick` | Quick CI: lint csr rtl test                       |
| `ci_full`  | Full CI: lint csr rtl formal test synth sta power pnr drc |
| `clean`    | Clean all subdirectories                          |
| `help`     | Show available targets                            |

